    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce paid bereavement leave as an employment right",
        "additional_details": "Introduce paid bereavement leave as an employment right\r\nLosing a loved one is traumatic, stressful & demanding, but there is no legal requirement for employers to provide paid bereavement leave.\r\n\r\nThis means employers can force people to immediately return to work or go unpaid/use their holiday, which is unacceptable & counter-productive for well-being.",
